# Wordtree -- An Interactive Visual Corpus Interface.

Incompatible with ruby 2.4, Active Record throws error as Arel::Visitors::SQLite has been deprecated.

## Getting Started

Use the rake command admin:reset to ingest and process corpus.

## Dependencies

- SQLite
- Redis

## Data Structure

- Words (symbols)
- Documents > Sentences > Word Intances in a linear ordering (coordinates).
- Directed, cyclic graph of sentence/word orderings 

words = nodes
each edge has it's own identity
pseudograph: cycles, loops